{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Playground logging can generate, at a minimum, a structured description"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of any type. If you want to provide a custom description of your type to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"logged in place of the default description, conform to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Playground logging generates a richer, more specialized description of core"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"types. For example, the contents of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"String"},{"type":"text","text":" are logged, as are the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"components of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSColor"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIColor"},{"type":"text","text":". The current playground logging"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implementation logs specialized descriptions of at least the following"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"types:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"String"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"NSString","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"Int","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UInt"},{"type":"text","text":", and the other standard library integer types"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Float"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Double"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Bool"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Date"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"NSDate","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSAttributedString"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"NSRange","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"URL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"NSURL","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"CGPoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"CGSize","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"CGRect","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSColor"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIColor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CGColor"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"code":"CIColor","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSImage"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"CGImage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"CIImage","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"NSBezierPath","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIBezierPath","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSView"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIView","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Playground logging may also be able to support specialized descriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of other types."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Conforming-to-the-CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible-Protocol","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Conforming to the CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible Protocol"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To add "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"},{"type":"text","text":" conformance to your custom type,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implement the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"playgroundDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" property. If your implementation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returns an instance of one of the types above, that type’s specialized"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"description is used. If you return any other type, a structured description"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is generated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your type has value semantics, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"playgroundDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"unaffected by subsequent mutations, if possible."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your type’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"playgroundDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" returns an instance which itself"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforms to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"},{"type":"text","text":", then that type’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"playgroundDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used, and so on. To prevent infinite loops,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"playground logging implementations can place a reasonable limit on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"kind of chaining."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["/documentation/swift/customplaygrounddisplayconvertible"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"}],"symbolKind":"protocol","externalID":"s:s34CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertibleP","modules":[{"name":"Swift"}],"roleHeading":"Protocol","title":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible","role":"symbol"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Customizing Your Type’s Reflection","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/CustomReflectable","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/CustomLeafReflectable","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/PlaygroundQuickLook","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/DebugDescription()"],"anchor":"Customizing-Your-Types-Reflection"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible"},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible/playgroundDescription"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that supplies a custom description for playground logging."}],"references":{"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/DebugDescription()":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/DebugDescription()","type":"topic","title":"DebugDescription()","kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift/debugdescription()","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"macro"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DebugDescription"},{"te